# Default agent runtime: Railway

For work in this repo, use **My Machines → railway-AutoTube** (self-hosted on Railway), not Cursor cloud.

Website: [cursor.com/agents](https://cursor.com/agents) with machine **railway-AutoTube**.

After Railway redeploy: `node ~/Projects/cursor-railway-worker/scripts/pin-default-workers.mjs` (Cursor quit first).
